g.text: When the Pan-American highway stops the journey cost increasesexpontially both physically and fiscally as migrants take boats and hire guides that help them through the unforgiving jungle.
Once the migrants make to Capurguna, Colombia they pay $50 for help walking across the Panamá border to Armila.
